528
00:30:30,280 --> 00:30:32,079
Hledala jsem spis Yan Zhiyuna.

529
00:30:32,479 --> 00:30:33,400
Yan Zhiyuna?

530
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:35,800
Jo!

531
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:39,000
Populární hráč v Tengyuan,

532
00:30:40,119 --> 00:30:41,239
