552
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:41,479
Zkus to.

553
00:31:43,199 --> 00:31:43,680
Miř na papír!

554
00:31:45,560 --> 00:31:46,079
Trefa.

555
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:47,560
Pěkná práce.

556
00:31:51,359 --> 00:31:51,880
Počkej,

557
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:53,839
zelenáči,

558
00:31:54,359 --> 00:31:56,079
