653
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,479
To ne.

654
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:55,800
Zase klameš!

655
00:37:56,120 --> 00:37:57,560
Blafuješ! Lhářko!

656
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:58,199
Au. To bolí.

657
00:37:58,239 --> 00:37:58,679
Poslouchej!

658
00:37:59,639 --> 00:38:00,159
Neboj se.

